# folhas
Text editor for reactive writing and documents sharing on social networks

# Group User
Manage users in **folhas API**

## User Collection [/user]
### Create a user [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "user": {
            "name": "Thiago Henrique Poiani",
            "email": "thpoiani@folhas.com",
            "password": "password"
          }
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
          "name": "Thiago Henrique Poiani",
          "email": "thpoiani@folhas.com",
          "password": "$2a$10$xmGzX2qUbLiQGkK68hhpGu0qKMv3rcNdX8q8s3CZQJ1wN3Tg4dlJW",
          "isActive": true,
          "createdAt": "2014-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
          "updatedAt": "2014-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",
          "id": "53802e02426b490b1c60a5c3"
        }

## Profile [/user/{email}/{?client_id}]
### Update a user [PUT]
+ Parameters
    + email (required, email, `thpoiani@folhas.com`) ... `email` of the User to perform action with.
    + client_id (required, string, `53802e02426b490b1c60a5c3`) ... `client_id` of the User to perform action with.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "user": {
                "name": "Thiago Poiani",
                "email": "thpoiani@folhas.com"
            }
        }

