# Group Document
Manage user's documents in **folhas API**

## Document Collection [/document/{?client_id}]
### Create a document [POST]
+ Parameters
    + client_id (required, string, `53802e02426b490b1c60a5c3`) ... `client_id` of the User to perform action with.

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
          "author": "thpoiani@folhas.com",
          "hash": "PyJBAR0LXM",
          "title": "Untitled document",
          "text": "",
          "isActive": true,
          "createdAt": "2014-01-05T00:00:00.000Z",
          "updatedAt": "2014-01-05T00:00:00.000Z",
          "id": "53804c097c6ea8e726e17192"
        }
        
